37163>>>>>    Function SetUserPassword String sLoginName String sPassword Returns Boolean
37165>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37165>>>>>        Integer iErr
37165>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37166>>>>>        
37166>>>>>        //  Find the user
37166>>>>>        Send Clear of hoUserDD
37167>>>>>        Move sLoginName to WebAppUser.LoginName
37168>>>>>        Send Find of hoUserDD EQ Index.1
37169>>>>>        If (not(Found)) Begin
37171>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37172>>>>>            Function_Return False
37173>>>>>        End
37173>>>>>>
37173>>>>>        
37173>>>>>        If (not(CreatePasswordHash(Self, Trim(sPassword), &sPassword))) Begin
37175>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37176>>>>>            Function_Return False
37177>>>>>        End
37177>>>>>>
37177>>>>>        Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.Password to sPassword
37178>>>>>        Get Request_Validate of hoUserDD to iErr
37179>>>>>        If (iErr) Begin
37181>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37182>>>>>            Function_Return False
37183>>>>>        End
37183>>>>>>
37183>>>>>        
37183>>>>>        Send Request_Save of hoUserDD
37184>>>>>        Function_Return (not(Err))
37185>>>>>    End_Function
