37197>>>>>    
37197>>>>>    //
37197>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37197>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37197>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37197>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37197>>>>>    //
37197>>>>>    // Params:
37197>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37197>>>>>    //
37197>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37199>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37199>>>>>        
37199>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37200>>>>>        
37200>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37200>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37202>>>>>            Set psUsername to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37203>>>>>            Set psLoginName to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37204>>>>>            Set piUserRights to WebAppUser.Rights
37205>>>>>            
37205>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37206>>>>>        End
37206>>>>>>
37206>>>>>        Else Begin
37207>>>>>            Set psUsername to ""
37208>>>>>            Set psLoginName to ""
37209>>>>>            Set piUserRights to 0
37210>>>>>            
37210>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37211>>>>>        End
37211>>>>>>
37211>>>>>    End_Procedure
37212>>>>>    
37212>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37214>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37214>>>>>    End_Procedure
37215>>>>>    
37215>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37217>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37217>>>>>    End_Procedure
37218>>>>>    
37218>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37220>>>>>        Integer iErr
37220>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37220>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37220>>>>>        
37220>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37221>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37222>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37224>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37226>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37227>>>>>        End
37227>>>>>>
37227>>>>>            
37227>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37227>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37228>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37229>>>>>        
37229>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37230>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37232>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37233>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37234>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37236>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37236>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37237>>>>>>
37237>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37238>>>>>            End
37238>>>>>>
37238>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37239>>>>>        End
37239>>>>>>
37239>>>>>    End_Procedure
37240>>>>>
37240>>>>>End_Class
